                        <lem><gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> paḻuvēṭṭaraiyar</lem>
                        <note>It should be noted that the text provided in NK 1977, no. 144 cannot read the word which precedes the title Paḻuvēṭṭaraiyar, while the summary of the ARE 1911, no. 90 proposes without hesitation Vāṇappaṭi, rendering thus the Paḻuvēṭṭaraiyar of Vāṇappaṭi. The inscription may have been in a better state in 1911 than in 1977, which would explain the clear reading of ARE.</note>
